<para style="p">

  <verse number="1" style="v" />Paul, a servant of God and an apostle of Jesus Christ, for the faith of God's chosen people and the knowledge of the truth that agrees with godliness.

  <verse number="2" style="v" />These are in the confidence of everlasting life that God, who is without lies, promised before all the ages of time.

  <verse number="3" style="v" />At the right time, he revealed his word by the message that he trusted me to deliver. I was to do this by the command of God our Savior.
